{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [
    {}
  ],
  "wsWinStyles": [
    {}
  ],
  "wpWinPositions": [
    {}
  ],
  "events": [
    {
      "tStartMs": 120,
      "dDurationMs": 4840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Skin lightening or bleaching is\na multibillion-dollar industry."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 4960,
      "dDurationMs": 4040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What is spoken about less these days\nis the harm some of these products"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 9000,
      "dDurationMs": 5200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "can have, both mentally and physically,\non lots of women out there."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 14200,
      "dDurationMs": 5280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Nowadays, many women use these creams\nfor cosmetic and cultural reasons."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 19480,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "In fact, Nigerian women use\nskin whitening products more"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 22760,
      "dDurationMs": 2280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "than any other African country."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 25040,
      "dDurationMs": 3880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "77% of women\nuse them there regularly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 28920,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "That's according\nto the UN World Health Organization."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 32120,
      "dDurationMs": 2840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "But what's being done\nto educate people about the risks?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 34960,
      "dDurationMs": 2160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "That's what we're getting into\nin today's episode."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 37280,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I'm Iqra Farooq and this is What in\nthe World from the BBC World Service."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 46040,
      "dDurationMs": 3600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So let's find out a little bit more\nabout these skin whitening products"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 49640,
      "dDurationMs": 3360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and how lots\nof women have been affected by them,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 53000,
      "dDurationMs": 1880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and have really experienced the risks."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 54880,
      "dDurationMs": 6280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nI'm joined by the BBC's Madina Maishanu,\nwho's in Abuja. Hey, Madina!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 61160,
      "dDurationMs": 3040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Hi Iqra, how are you?\nI'm not too bad!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 64200,
      "dDurationMs": 2800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Madina, I know you've been doing lots\nof reporting on this,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 67000,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and you have spoken\nto one mother, right?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 69880,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Who's really experienced the harm\nof these skin,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 72760,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "these skin whitening products?\nYes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 75640,
      "dDurationMs": 5080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I spoke to a certain mother who is\nin her mid-30s."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 80720,
      "dDurationMs": 1960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "We named her Fatima,\nbut that's not her real name."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 82680,
      "dDurationMs": 3320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "We just did that to protect her identity."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 86000,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So Fatima is someone who bleached six"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 90280,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "of her children,\nwhich is a really large number."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 92960,
      "dDurationMs": 4960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So when I met Fatima\nin a northern state in Nigeria,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 97920,
      "dDurationMs": 4680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "she told me how she bleached six of her\nchildren and she told me why she did it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 102600,
      "dDurationMs": 3960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So what she told me is\nshe faced pressure from her family"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 106560,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and discrimination,\nparticularly from her mother."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 109440,
      "dDurationMs": 2960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Her mother does not show love to any\nof her children"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 112400,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "because her children were\ndark skinned."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 115000,
      "dDurationMs": 2080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And she has a particular sister,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 117080,
      "dDurationMs": 2280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and the sister married\na light skinned man,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 119360,
      "dDurationMs": 2640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "so her sister's children are\nlight skinned."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 122000,
      "dDurationMs": 4760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So anytime they go to visit their\ngrandmother, she and her sister,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 126760,
      "dDurationMs": 4480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "when they bring their kids to visit\ntheir grandmother, they notice that"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 131240,
      "dDurationMs": 4600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "the grandmother shows love\nto the light skinned children."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 135840,
      "dDurationMs": 840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They don't show..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 136680,
      "dDurationMs": 4680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "She doesn't show love to Fatima's\nchildren, which kind of broke her heart,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 141360,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and it pushed her\nto make that terrible decision."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 144560,
      "dDurationMs": 3320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I can say that to this date,\nshe is still facing the stigma."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 147880,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "She and her children\nare still facing the stigma"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 150360,
      "dDurationMs": 4920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "because one of her daughters can't go\nout with her face open, because"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 155280,
      "dDurationMs": 5880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "she has discoloured lips and people\noften mistaken her for a drug user."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 161160,
      "dDurationMs": 6160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "You know, when you use drugs,\nthe smoke, the cigarettes,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 167320,
      "dDurationMs": 3680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "the chemicals or the things\nthat people like drug users take,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 171000,
      "dDurationMs": 4040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "it can affect the colour on their lips."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 175040,
      "dDurationMs": 2720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So her daughter has\nvery discoloured lips."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 177760,
      "dDurationMs": 2720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And when people see her outside,\nthey start chanting, oh,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 180480,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "this is a drug user,\nthis is a drug user."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 183080,
      "dDurationMs": 3240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So due to that, her daughter\ncan't go out with her face open."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 186320,
      "dDurationMs": 3160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "She uses what\nin Islam we call a niqab."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 189480,
      "dDurationMs": 2000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "It's something\nthat you use to cover your face."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 191480,
      "dDurationMs": 2240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Only your eyes can show."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 193720,
      "dDurationMs": 3080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So she uses that to go out\nand her little baby,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 196800,
      "dDurationMs": 4720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "who is barely two years old.\nShe also bleached him."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 201520,
      "dDurationMs": 3360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So due to bleaching him, which\nFatima did,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 204880,
      "dDurationMs": 2920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "his skin barrier is weakened"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 207800,
      "dDurationMs": 3040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and that is one of the side effects\nof using bleaching creams."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 210840,
      "dDurationMs": 6840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Your skin can become thinner and\nif you have a wound, it will take longer to heal."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 217680,
      "dDurationMs": 2800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So I can say\nthat they are still facing..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 220480,
      "dDurationMs": 1800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they are still facing issues"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 222280,
      "dDurationMs": 3000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nbecause of, you know,\nwhat Fatima did to her children."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 225280,
      "dDurationMs": 3880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Just tell me a little bit more about\nthe kinds of products she was using."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 229160,
      "dDurationMs": 7320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So Fatima was using creams that you\ncould access at any random supermarket."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 236480,
      "dDurationMs": 4400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "These creams had different chemicals inside them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 240880,
      "dDurationMs": 4560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Like kojic acid, like hydroquinone,\nlike mercury,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 245440,
      "dDurationMs": 4480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and different types of steroids\nthat are dangerous to the skin"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 249920,
      "dDurationMs": 3480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and to a person's health\nif used in high quantity."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 253400,
      "dDurationMs": 2400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So most of these creams\nshe was using,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 255800,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they had double or triple\nof the approved dosage in them,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 260080,
      "dDurationMs": 4760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "which was quite harmful for adults\nnot even to talk about children."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 264840,
      "dDurationMs": 5040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "When I spoke to Nigeria's food\nand drug agency regulator, Nafdac,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 269880,
      "dDurationMs": 3520,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they told me that these chemicals\nthat I mentioned at the beginning,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 273400,
      "dDurationMs": 3640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "kojic acid, hydroquinone,\nthere is an approved dosage."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 277040,
      "dDurationMs": 4480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "For example, for kojic acid it is 1%.\nKojic acid is not bad."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 281520,
      "dDurationMs": 4800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Kojic acid is something that you\ncan use to treat hyperpigmentation,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 286320,
      "dDurationMs": 3920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "dermatitis and other skin conditions."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 290240,
      "dDurationMs": 5320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "But it's just the fact that people\nabuse these chemicals in the creams."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 295560,
      "dDurationMs": 1600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They use a higher dosage."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 297160,
      "dDurationMs": 3160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "How easy is it to get a hold\nof these creams in Nigeria?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 300320,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "It is very, very easy\nto get these creams in Nigeria."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 303520,
      "dDurationMs": 2440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "You can walk into any supermarket"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 305960,
      "dDurationMs": 4440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and find adult bleaching creams,\nbaby bleaching creams,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 310400,
      "dDurationMs": 3160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "you can even find these creams..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 313560,
      "dDurationMs": 2320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "you can even find\nthe raw chemicals"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 315880,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "when you go to the market. Randomly\nyou can find them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 318560,
      "dDurationMs": 5400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Because when I went to Kano, where\nI did the story, I went to one"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 323960,
      "dDurationMs": 4600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "of the markets where these creams are\nreadily and easily available."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 328560,
      "dDurationMs": 5280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So there's a whole row of shops\nin that market where I found that"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 333840,
      "dDurationMs": 5760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "these people just use these chemicals\nand mix them; the raw chemicals."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 339600,
      "dDurationMs": 3520,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "You can just walk in and tell them,\nI want a certain percentage"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 343120,
      "dDurationMs": 3640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "of this chemical, mix with\nthis chemical, mix with this chemical"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 346760,
      "dDurationMs": 5080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "to make me light skinned in,\nfor example, let's say a week."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 351840,
      "dDurationMs": 3560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So they are very available\nanywhere you go to you can find them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 355400,
      "dDurationMs": 3760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And how does that compare\nto other countries in Africa?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 359160,
      "dDurationMs": 3040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Is it a similar situation,\nvery widely available?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 362520,
      "dDurationMs": 4000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Well, when we talk about other countries,\nlike you mentioned in your cue,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 366560,
      "dDurationMs": 5800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Nigeria is the top African country\nwhere people bleach their skin"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 372360,
      "dDurationMs": 3640,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "with about 77%.\nBut followed by Nigeria"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 376000,
      "dDurationMs": 2920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "there's Congo-Brazzaville,\nthere's Senegal,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 378920,
      "dDurationMs": 5080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "there's Ghana with about 60%,\n50% and 30 something percent."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 384000,
      "dDurationMs": 1760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "These are just a few countries."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 385760,
      "dDurationMs": 3960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So bleaching or skin lightening is\nsomething that is done widespread"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 389720,
      "dDurationMs": 3560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "in places like Africa\nand not only Africa."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 393280,
      "dDurationMs": 3280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "In other countries,\nlike in Asian countries too."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 396560,
      "dDurationMs": 4080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "In India too. So it's something that\nhappens in many parts of the world,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 400640,
      "dDurationMs": 4520,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "but particularly in Africa.\nIt's something that people do a lot."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 405160,
      "dDurationMs": 2200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Madina, I know it's a big question,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 407360,
      "dDurationMs": 5120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "but why do women feel\nthe need to use these creams?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 412480,
      "dDurationMs": 4720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So the few women I came across\nwhen I was doing this piece,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 417200,
      "dDurationMs": 5720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they showed me how\nusually they grew up understanding"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 422920,
      "dDurationMs": 5120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "that light skin is being linked\nto wealth,"
