      "tStartMs": 437920,
      "dDurationMs": 4800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "you have a good life.\nYou are enjoying in life."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 442720,
      "dDurationMs": 4520,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So that's why a lot of women and even\nmen they want to bleach their skin."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 447240,
      "dDurationMs": 3400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "They want to have\nthat beautiful appearance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 450640,
      "dDurationMs": 2600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "It's also,\nI think it's something that started"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 453240,
      "dDurationMs": 3520,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "It's the whole\nsocietal pressure because"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 456760,
      "dDurationMs": 5240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "the fact that people link these good\nthings to light skinned women or men,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 462000,
      "dDurationMs": 5560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "it has become a thing of whenever\nsomeone wants to get married,"
