    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 470160,
      "dDurationMs": 1880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "your family\nmight reject the person.\n "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 472160,
      "dDurationMs": 6600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So people link being light skinned\nto having it all in life\n "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 478800,
      "dDurationMs": 1960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "or having some sort of enjoyment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 480800,
      "dDurationMs": 2240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So that's why a lot\nof people who are dark skinned,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 483040,
      "dDurationMs": 3440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "they'd rather use those creams\neven though they know the harm"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 486480,
      "dDurationMs": 4680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "that they might cause them\nthan face stigma in life."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 491160,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Let's take a step back for a second\nand have a look"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 493840,
      "dDurationMs": 2360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "at how skin\nlightening products actually work,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 496200,
      "dDurationMs": 3320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and a little bit\nof the science behind it all as well."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 499520,
      "dDurationMs": 3400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "We've got Zainab Bashir,\nwho owns a dermatology clinic"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 502920,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "in Abuja in Nigeria, on the line."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 505600,
      "dDurationMs": 2920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Hey, Zainab.\nHi. Nice to meet you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 508520,
      "dDurationMs": 2040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Thanks for having me.\nSo, Zainab,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 510560,
      "dDurationMs": 3360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "what is actually happening to the\nskin when these products are used?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 514360,
      "dDurationMs": 5320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So just for the context of a layman,\nwhen you apply these bleaching products,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 519680,
      "dDurationMs": 4680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "it technically rips off\nthe hydrophilic layer of the skin,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 524360,
      "dDurationMs": 2840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "which is the protective layer\nof the skin."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 527200,
      "dDurationMs": 3680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "In that sense,\nthe skin gets easily susceptible"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 530880,
      "dDurationMs": 3880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "to damages, to infection."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 534840,
      "dDurationMs": 4480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And the bad part is some\nof these ingredients in the skin."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 539320,
      "dDurationMs": 4920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "lightening products have travellers so it\ncan get absorbed into your bloodstream."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 544240,
      "dDurationMs": 5040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So it's a very potent drug, which\nare the steroids that can get absorbed"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 549280,
      "dDurationMs": 4040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "into your bloodstream and even affect\nother organs in your body."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 553320,
      "dDurationMs": 4040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And what kind of ingredients are we\ntalking about which are really harmful?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 557360,
      "dDurationMs": 5480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So the most common that we find\naround are steroids, potent steroids:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 562840,
      "dDurationMs": 3720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "clobetasol propionate,\nwhich is a very common one."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 566560,
      "dDurationMs": 4560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Another very common ingredient is hydroquinone,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 571120,
      "dDurationMs": 4760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "which is used\nin outrageous amounts."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 575880,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "I mean, these skin lightening products,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 578360,
      "dDurationMs": 4120,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nanother hazardous ingredient which is\nalso very popular is mercury."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 582480,
      "dDurationMs": 4320,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So these three ingredients combined\nactually cause a lot of problems"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 586920,
      "dDurationMs": 4080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and a lot of hazards on the skin\nand even in internal organs."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 591000,
      "dDurationMs": 3360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And I wondered if we could touch on\nthose side effects a little bit more."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 594360,
      "dDurationMs": 2960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What sort of side effects\nare you seeing in your clinic?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 597320,
      "dDurationMs": 2200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So we've had like severe cases"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 599520,
      "dDurationMs": 4160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "with patients who have used\nbleaching products for over a decade."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 603680,
      "dDurationMs": 4080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Most of them start bleaching from\na very young age, from teenage years,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 607760,
      "dDurationMs": 2680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "or some of them even from a younger"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 610440,
      "dDurationMs": 3360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "toddler age that their mothers\nhave been bleaching them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 613800,
      "dDurationMs": 4000,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Some of the severe cases we've seen\nis a thinning of the skin,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 617800,
      "dDurationMs": 3160,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "in a sense\nthat you can literally see the veins"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 620960,
      "dDurationMs": 2920,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "on the skin\nbecause of how thin it is."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 623880,
      "dDurationMs": 5240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Another adverse effect with skin\nbleaching is exogenous ochronosis."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 629120,
      "dDurationMs": 3960,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Now, exogenous ochronosis is\na condition"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 633080,
      "dDurationMs": 2800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "where the skin turns bluish black"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 635880,
      "dDurationMs": 5280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "because of continuous usage\nof steroids or mercury over time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 641160,
      "dDurationMs": 3200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Now when that happens,\nit's more like a first degree burn."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 644360,
      "dDurationMs": 5440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So the skin is completely damaged,\nsometimes almost irreversible,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 649800,
      "dDurationMs": 6480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and it forms a thick layer\non your skin that looks bluish."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 656280,
      "dDurationMs": 4360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So those are some of the severe cases\nbesides the now upcoming cases"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 660640,
      "dDurationMs": 6360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "of melanoma and squamous cell carcinoma,\nwhich is a form of skin cancer."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 667000,
      "dDurationMs": 2760,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "It's been so good to have you on.\nThank you, Zainab."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 669760,
      "dDurationMs": 1600,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "No problem. Thank you so much."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 671360,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": " \nAnd, Madina, back to you now."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 673840,
      "dDurationMs": 4040,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What about when it comes\nto the Nigerian authorities?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 677920,
      "dDurationMs": 2400,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "What are they doing\nto kind of raise awareness"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 680320,
      "dDurationMs": 2720,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "of the risks\nbehind these skin lightning creams?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 683040,
      "dDurationMs": 2480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So regarding the Nigerian authorities,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 685520,
      "dDurationMs": 5240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "like I mentioned before, Nafdac, the\nNigerian Food and Drug Agency body"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 690760,
      "dDurationMs": 6280,
      "segs": [
