      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 697040,
      "dDurationMs": 4080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "on bleaching creams,\non the use of bleaching creams."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 701120,
      "dDurationMs": 4240,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So that kind of raised awareness\nin many parts of the country"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 705360,
      "dDurationMs": 4280,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "about the dangers of bleaching cream\nand how widespread the issue is."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 709640,
      "dDurationMs": 1680,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And apart from that,"
        }
